<b>Average reputation</b><br />
Measures the Volume and Score over a period of time for: <br />
<li>Sender address</li>
<li>Sender domain</li>
<li>Sender IP</li>
<li>Client name</li>
<li>Fingerprints and more.</li>
<br />
FORMULA<br />
Incremented Score / Incremented Volume >= Average reputation<br />
When Incremented Score divided by Incremented Volume<br />
is greater than (or equal to) Average reputation value<br />
then the SMTP connection is not accepted.<br />
